# CI lint/test tooling (a dev-dependency): the Linterpol image bundles the linters used here
# (hadolint, actionlint, shellcheck, biome) plus container-structure-test. Not shipped in the images.
# Single source for the pin, read by scripts/test.sh and the build-image.yml structure-test step.
# Pinned by digest; Renovate bumps it (.github/renovate.jsonc, PRs labeled dev-dependencies).
# renovate: datasource=docker depName=ghcr.io/lahaluhem/linterpol
LINTERPOL_IMAGE=ghcr.io/lahaluhem/linterpol:latest@sha256:055db962210189c3d7520c692c05ae53f19632ae81ff0bb082722b0cd172466d
